  <title>A rapid technique for screening banana cultivars for resistance to Xanthomonas wilt</title>
  <URL>https://cn.bing.com/academic/profile?id=e1a81a91a0c83cb73f09b8e2a1228511&amp;encoded=0&amp;v=paper_preview&amp;mkt=zh-cn</URL>
